               <div class="writofest-image"></div>
               <p class="big" style="color:rgb(223, 223, 223);line-height: 2.3rem;" >WritoFest is a National Level Annual Literary
                Fest and signature event of Scriptink, comprising of two events, one of which being
                a Writing Competition event, 'Ink your script' and
                a LIVE talk show by famous authors/poets/speakers of all four languages
                 from different states, 'Mic of Motivation'.
                <br>In the writing competition, the participants will write
                and submit through the portal in android app on the given themes and compete against each other, choosing any form of writing
                 (Quote, Poetry, Article or Story) and writing in any one of the language (English, Hindi, Kannada or Urdu). 
                 There are equal rewards for all categories and all langauges.<br>
                'Mic of Motivation' is for Speakers, Writers,
                and Poets to guide, share their insights with
                the participants along with recitations of their
                writings and motivate the participants.
                We encourage and inspire more women to
                pursue it and be a part of it.
                Let the weekend be full of Joy, learning, exposure
                to how professional think, express in form of
                literature and lifetime experience of meet. It is a
                full day event. 
            <br><br>
            Grab the opportunity to acknowledge, support and witness the National Level Literary Fest being a participator of it.</p>
  
                 <br><br>
            <h4 class="event-heading">SPEAKERS & CHIEF GUESTS</h4>
            <div class="guest-container">
               
                <div class="guest-info">
                    <div class="guest-image-container">
                        <img class="guest-image" src="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ys_s1FND-iQ/WmrAK5zQCYI/AAAAAAAAGJc/dORv2vMfT7w2Ud7qn07mz0fDMRB8_AI4ACLcBGAs/s1600/31441001132_8187f77314_b.jpg" alt="guest image">
                        <h2 class="heading-posts">Doddarange Gowda</h2>
                    </div>
                   
                   
                    <div class="guest-about">
                        <h3 class="about-heading">ABOUT</h3>
                        <p class="small">
                            In his long Journey of Writing he has published 48 anthologies of  ODES. 6 Ballets (Dance – Dramas), 5 Life Sketches Ballets (Biographies), 29 anthologies of Critical Essays, 4 Travelogues, 2 Criticisms in Kannada Language, besides innumerable literary articles in Vernacular Journals and Periodicals.
                            He has penned lyrics for more than 500 songs with many achieving critical acclaim and awards. He has written dialogues for more than 10 films and has scripted over 100 tele-serials.
He has been awarded Padmashree Award in 2018 and many state awards.Since1st of August 1997 the American Biographical Institute of USA has appointed Dr.DoddarangeGowda as an Indian councillor. This is a great honour and recognition given by ABI USA for humble and simple Kannada writer.


                        </p>
                        <a id="guest-anchor" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Doddarange_Gowda"><i class="fa fa fa-wikipedia-w "></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="guest-info">
                    <div class="guest-image-container">
