                        <h2 class="heading-posts">Shambhu Shikhar</h2>
                    </div>
                   
                   
                    <div class="guest-about">
                        <h3 class="about-heading">ABOUT</h3>
                        <p class="small"> 
                            He achieved the status of semi-finalist of renowned TV show "The Great Indian Laughter Challenge-3", he can also be seen very frequently in a popular political TV show on News 18 India named "Lapete Mein Netaji" as well.
He is a regular columnist in sociopolitical magazine Sopan-Step. His articles, poems and satires are being regularly published with various newspapers and magazines. He has recited poem more than 1000 kavi-sammelans all over the country. He is the winner of Delhi HansodDangal aired on AajTak.

                        </p>
                        <a id="guest-anchor" href=" https://www.facebook.com/KaviShambhuShikhar/"><i class="fa fa fa-facebook-f "></i></a>
